import { faCartShopping, faCircleInfo, faHouseChimney, faList } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons'
import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/react-fontawesome'
import { Box, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'
import NavbarItem from './NavbarItem'

const Navbar = () => {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ boxShadow: "9px 9px 20px -4px rgba(0,0,0,0.57)" }} display="flex"
      height="64px" justifyContent="center" backgroundColor="rgb(2, 0, 36)"
      linearGradient="90deg, rgba(2, 0, 36, 1) 0%, rgba(153, 189, 247, 1) 0%, rgba(142, 142, 236, 1) 73%"
    >

      <Box
        display="flex"
        height="64px"
        alignItems="center"
        justifyContent="space-between"
        padding="0 10px"
        maxWidth="1248px"
        width="100%"

      >Logo

        <Box display="flex"
          gap="20px"
        >
          <NavbarItem icon={faHouseChimney} name="Home"></NavbarItem>
          <NavbarItem icon={faCircleInfo} name="About"></NavbarItem>
          <NavbarItem icon={faCartShopping} name="Bucket"></NavbarItem>
          <NavbarItem icon={faList} name="packge"></NavbarItem>

          {/* <Typography variant='body1'><FontAwesomeIcon icon={faHouseChimney}></FontAwesomeIcon> Home</Typography>
        <Typography variant='body1'><FontAwesomeIcon icon={faCircleInfo}></FontAwesomeIcon> About</Typography>
        <Typography variant='body1'><FontAwesomeIcon icon={faCartShopping}></FontAwesomeIcon> Bucket</Typography>
        <Typography variant='body1'><FontAwesomeIcon icon={faList}></FontAwesomeIcon> packege</Typography> */}
        </Box>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default Navbar
